generator = EmpiricalBayesThompsonSampler(min_weight=0.0)
generator.fit(Xs=[x[:-1] for x in self.Xs], Ys=[y[:-1] for y in self.Ys],
    Yvars=[y[:-1] for y in self.Yvars], parameter_values=self.
    parameter_values, outcome_names=self.outcome_names)
arms, weights, _ = generator.gen(n=5, parameter_values=self.
    parameter_values, objective_weights=np.array([1, 0]))
self.assertEqual(arms, [[3, 3], [2, 2], [1, 1]])
for weight, expected_weight in zip(weights, [0.74, 0.21, 0.05]):
    self.assertAlmostEqual(weight, expected_weight, 1)
